{"tid":1537334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝暴徒罷搭港鐵！","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:44:41.000Z","uid":313681,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b28c793a31b2325798041e8215801aa1520087b4","tid":1537334,"uid":313681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"搞到地鐵冇人搭，站站都有位坐<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>益晒我地愛國愛黨嘅市民</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你地千其唔好全民跳閘呀</span></strong><br />\n如果你地個個都跳,<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定每個市民都學你地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n琴日見到暴徒文宣，真系好恐怖<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原來跳閘系咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oy0wjGK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOy0wjGK.jpg&h=b403d40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果日日都全民跳閘，港鐵會倒閉架</span></strong><br />\n求下你地唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3841b4c2695c9490d2139b16cf4b741f2ce88c70","tid":1537334,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:42:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f11894bb2397196e4f9cb36525962aaf338fd565","tid":1537334,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8W7Cuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8W7Cuk.jpg&h=a399d20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"e642f2ddddb3aeca89ace2b555c8d2ec3634eb73","tid":1537334,"uid":52727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3DMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=1e5c5455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa6e23787b166e39a974d87400b81c650d80e35","tid":1537334,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}